README for HW2 solution of CMPS12B.

C. Seshadhri, Sept 2017
=====================================

Solution files
-------------------
(Class files for chesspieces): ChessPiece.java, Bishop.java, Knight.java, Pawn.java, King.java, Queen.java, Rook.java
(Other files): Node.java, Utilities.java
(Main files): ChessBoard.java, Makefile, README

=====================================

Instruction to run solution
--------------------------------------
Let $ denote the prompt.

$ make 

Creates ChessBoard.jar

$ java -jar ChessBoard.java <input file> <output file>

Check out ChessBoard.java for documentation on format for input and output

For example:

$ java -jar ChessBoard.jar test-input.txt output.txt

The file output.txt should be identical to test-output.txt.

$ make clean

This removes all jar and class files.
